工程師第一季果陣既攻勢比較上係最好睇<br />\n即係搶左利冠軍果季<br />\n都入左最多波好似13幾球定幾多唔知有無記錯"},{"pid":"ac496cd98e83f3cadce0e3833263986d908ed7d0","tid":291404,"uid":46035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/11OOAQSnUaZT2M/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F11OOAQSnUaZT2M%2Fgiphy.gif&h=8d71f2ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係想引戰<br />\n睇波為開心。咁樣咁多限制，呢樣正統，呢樣威d為咩<br />\n好似阿成日話洗錢小，貴一貴買年青球員，好值得自豪我都覺，唔洗成日屌車曼炒貴，因為大家球隊目標唔同<br />\n你享受收支平衡同埋有限資源買野既滿足感<br />\n<br />\n又好似曼成日笑阿車鏝小冠<br />\n利又比人抽成地精<br />\n講笑無問題但如果真係好認真咁樣憎對方一隊波就好有問題<br />\n<br />\n利申我唔係混種big4迷</blockquote><br />\n我都有朋友係孫繼海時期已經捧曼城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec61185e18aff7fc75fd695236cdd25b271728d","tid":291404,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61ed585903b92b65132aee1d8787b2d48f54b312","tid":291404,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>曼城依家咪好似十幾年前既阿仙奴囉 <br />\n過多十年一定成堆人打飛機j緊個兩個英超冠軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇埋下季就知哥狗會唔會玩殘隊波</blockquote><br />\n爭氣d啦隊波 咪唔會比人笑"},{"pid":"dc8d57280386504876e2a87df41739c4739bba35","tid":291404,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"講咁多野何嘗唔係另一種認證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d14fe35ac25b6491032275ef1d530202bd5f92e","tid":291404,"uid":107755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/11OOAQSnUaZT2M/giphy.gif\"